Initial build: Monkey Maghees Node.js marketing site for Hostinger

Node.js Express app serving a 3D immersive marketing website for the
Monkey Maghees bar asset sale in Poughkeepsie, NY ($150,000).

- Express server with gzip compression and /health endpoint
- 19 real venue photos served via Cloudinary CDN (f_auto,q_auto)
- Three.js particle hero, GSAP scroll animations, infinite photo strip
- Sections: Numbers, Opportunity, Included, Gallery, Story, Location, CTA
- Mobile-first responsive, SEO meta tags, asset sale disclaimers
- Ready for Hostinger Node.js deployment via Git import

